Submodules¶

vlearn.classifiers.cnn3d module¶

class vlearn.classifiers.cnn3d.CNN3D¶

Bases: object

The following class provides standard 3DCNNs

(reimplementation) and an intuitive way to build custom neural networks using tensorflow 2.0.

Supported custom architectures are:

  1. single

  2. pyramid

  3. inverted pyramid

Supported standard architectures are:

  1. C3D
